original_font_information.description: Helvetica Now is the first comprehensive reworking of the Helvetica family in more than 35 years. It consists of three size ranges: Micro, Text and Display. Helvetica Now Display embodies the design lessons from six decades of Helvetica in use. It is a stunningly refined and thrillingly graceful series of designs for large sizes. From Hairline to Extra Black, these fonts are essential tools for optimal, beautiful display typesetting.
